NK092(khe)001:19284: de ltar gang gis bsal ba mdzad ce na /
NK092(khe)001:19285: don ji lta ba bzhin du riga cing mthong bar
NK092(khe)001:19286: byed pa'i gsung chos kyi 'brug sgra chen po dang
NK092(khe)001:19287: / gdul bya'i rgyud brlan pa'i chos kyi chara mang po phab pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19288: gdul bya'i blo rim 'dren pa'i chos kyi glu dbyangs
NK092(khe)001:19289: sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa sna tshogas dang
NK092(khe)001:19290: / gdul bya'i blo dang mthun par cir yang 'char
NK092(khe)001:19291: bas chos kyi gara thabs sna tshogas kyi mdzad pa
NK092(khe)001:19292: / dang / phyi nang gi chosa kyi mchoda pa sna tshogas mang po byung ste /
NK092(khe)001:19293: rgya khyon tshad med par 'byamsa klas pa'i nam mkha'a
NK092(khe)001:19294: phyi nang gsang gsum du bshad pa kun tu khyab
NK092(khe)001:19295: pa'i 'jig rten la chos kyi sgra tha dad pa
NK092(khe)001:19296: phyogs mtshams brgyad phan tshun dang /
NK092(khe)001:19298: thad ka'i phyogs mtshams s+n+rel zhi la sogas pa gdul
NK092(khe)001:19299: bya'i gnas thamsa cad du tha dad par ma khyab
NK092(khe)001:19300: pa med para gsang sngags ji lta bar snang ba
NK092(khe)001:19301: ma nges pas linga longa du dus phyad pa'am rtag
NK092(khe)001:19302: para don mdzad pa byung ngo //
NK092(khe)001:19303: 'gro ba'i ched du rmad du byung ba'i sku mchog
NK092(khe)001:19304: gi sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa ji ltar
NK092(khe)001:19305: yang snang ba'i sku re re la yang 'od zera
NK092(khe)001:19308: bsnol mar 'khrug cinga phyogs rnams su nges pa med
NK092(khe)001:19309: par linga longa du phyad de rtag tu don mdzad
NK092(khe)001:19310: do // bar 'dir chos rjes phyag mchan bzhugs pa'i dpe la /
NK092(khe)001:19311: ye shes rmad du byung ba'i sku yang lhun chags pas lhan ne'o //
NK092(khe)001:19312: zhes bzhugs kyang dpe gzhan dang 'grel chen du mi bzhugs /
NK092(khe)001:19313: rmada du byung ba'i thugs mchog rnam par mi rtog
NK092(khe)001:19314: bzhin du thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang shin
NK092(khe)001:19315: tu gsal bar lhang nge nyid du bzhugs pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19316: rmad du byung ba'i gsung theg pa chen po byin
NK092(khe)001:19317: rlabs kyi bstan pa mang po bsam gyis mi khyab
NK092(khe)001:19318: pa yanga dgyes pa'i a ho zhes sgrogsa shing chos
NK092(khe)001:19319: ston to // de'ang skye 'gag med pa'i don la dgyes pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19320: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs la dgyes pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19321: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas dapaga tu med pa
NK092(khe)001:19322: ji snyed pa yanga gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19323: sgra gcig tu mtshungs par gsang ba'i bdag po'i sku
NK092(khe)001:19324: gsung thugs la ngam pas e ma'o //
NK092(khe)001:19326: gsang ba'i mnga' bdag dam pas rmad du byung ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19327: theg pa chen po'i rola pa'i mdzad pa snang bas
NK092(khe)001:19328: chos kyi sgo theg pa mtha' dag gis 'gro ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19329: dona gyi snang ba yang dag par byung ngo //
NK092(khe)001:19331: rigs kyi bdag po nyid kyi nye ba'i 'khor 'bum phrag bcu dang /
NK092(khe)001:19332: ring ba'i 'khor gdul bya bsam pa sna tshogas tha
NK092(khe)001:19333: dad pa dag kyang gsang ba'i byin rlabs kyis rim
NK092(khe)001:19334: dang cig car du don la spro zhing mngon par
NK092(khe)001:19335: dga' ba'i ya mtshan sna tshogs kyis ngo matshara mchog
NK092(khe)001:19336: tu skyed / shes rab gong nas gong du 'phags pas riga pa'i rtsal sbyangsa /
NK092(khe)001:19337: rtogs pas dona gyi che ba mngon du phyung ste /
NK092(khe)001:19338: ston pa'i byin rlabs la shin tu ngam nas /
NK092(khe)001:19340: zhes sgrogs shing don la ngo matshara bar gyur te /
NK092(khe)001:19341: gdul bya thamsa cad ston pa la 'dun bas gsang ba'i don la nye bar gansa so //
NK092(khe)001:19342: rgyud kyi rtog pa zhi bar gnas so //
NK092(khe)001:19343: chos kyi don mthong nas gzhan gyi don spyod pa la dga' ba dang ldan para gansa so //
NK092(khe)001:19344: de dag sku gsung thugs kyi sgo nas gsol ba btab pa'i lan du ci rigs par sbyar ro //
NK092(khe)001:19348: chos nyid du zhi bar gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:19349: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19350: 'khor rnams snod du rung bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19351: de nas ston pa gasnga ba mchoga gi badga po desa /
NK092(khe)001:19352: nyid kyi 'khora rnams kyi sgrib pa rnam para sbyangsa shing dag par mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK092(khe)001:19353: skal ba med pa rnams mi gnas par byed cing /
NK092(khe)001:19354: skal ba can rnams spyan sngar 'du bar byed pa
NK092(khe)001:19355: nyid kyis dgongs pa'i mtshan nges pa rdo rjee rgyan
NK092(khe)001:19356: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzina la snyomsa para zhugsa
NK092(khe)001:19357: nasa / shangas kyi dbugs kyi h'u ringas lasa lta
NK092(khe)001:19358: ngan dang sgrib pa 'joms pa'i nus pa dang ldan
NK092(khe)001:19359: pas rdo rje mngona pa'i mthu can gyi sngags tshig
NK092(khe)001:19360: 'di daga gi sgra bton te mngona para phyung ngo
NK092(khe)001:19361: nasa / // h'u h'u h'u zhes rdo rje gsum gyi phyir grangs nges la /
NK092(khe)001:19362: rdo rje gsang ba'i gral 'dir 'adu bar dbang bas
NK092(khe)001:19363: 'dus pa yi 'khor gsang mchog thega pa chena po
NK092(khe)001:19364: rtogs par 'dod pas spyan sngar 'tshogs pa dama tshig
NK092(khe)001:19365: chen po sems dpa' rdo rje la sogs pa'i gsang
NK092(khe)001:19366: sngags kyi rigas can rnams ni rtogs pa gong 'og
NK092(khe)001:19367: ltar gral bla 'oga gi rima pa ji lta ba
NK092(khe)001:19368: bzhina du rdo rje gasnga ba'i gral 'dir 'khoda de
NK092(khe)001:19369: 'dug la / theg chen gsang sngags kyi rigas ma
NK092(khe)001:19370: yin pa ru tra can la sogs pa gsang ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19371: rigs meda pa'am min pa rnams ni rgyud 'dzin par
NK092(khe)001:19372: mi 'gyur bas gzhan du song zhig pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19374: las dang skal ba mchog gi spyod yul rigas can
NK092(khe)001:19375: rnams kyi dama tshigas dam pa gsang sngags zab mo
NK092(khe)001:19376: 'di ni / rigas dang skal ba med pa rnams
NK092(khe)001:19377: la 'abba ste rtogs par mi 'gyur bas dam tshig
NK092(khe)001:19378: gi don de lasa 'adsa shing nyams na de dag
NK092(khe)001:19379: ngan song du rgyud brlag par byed pas bskrad pa'o
NK092(khe)001:19380: 'di ni / // 'og gi 'od kyi phreng ba bzhi 'don pa'i sngags /
NK092(khe)001:19381: h'u kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK092(khe)001:19382: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK092(khe)001:19383: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK092(khe)001:19384: tsi ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK092(khe)001:19386: ston pa'i zhes ljagsa kyi dabnga poo'i 'od kyi me dpunga chen po las /
NK092(khe)001:19387: 'od bzhi byung ba ni phyi nang gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK092(khe)001:19390: rigs kyi he ru ka phra men dang bcas pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19391: khro bo 'oda kyi phrenga ba 'abra ba bar ma
NK092(khe)001:19393: rdo rje srin po khro bo bcu la sogs pa
NK092(khe)001:19394: 'od kyi phreng ba dang bcas par 'phro ba dang
NK092(khe)001:19395: / rdo rje gnod sbyin 'oda kyi phreng ba dang bcas pa bsnol mar 'khrug pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19396: za byed chen po ru ti te ru ka la
NK092(khe)001:19397: sogs pa 'od kyi phung po'i tshub ma rgyud mar
NK092(khe)001:19398: bar ma chad pa rnams byung basa skal med rnams
NK092(khe)001:19399: bskrad pa'o // de'ang dang po sku mdog nag po g.yas rdo rje /
NK092(khe)001:19400: gnyis pa sku mdog mthing nag ral gri /
NK092(khe)001:19401: gsum pa sku mdog ljang ku rdo rje rgya gram /
NK092(khe)001:19402: bzhi pa sku mdog dmar nag g.yas mi snying g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19407: sgo lnga bzhi po rigs skyes pas grol ba'o //
NK092(khe)001:19408: skal med dngos gang snyam pa la /
NK092(khe)001:19409: rgyud gcig pa dang tha dad pa gnyis ka sbyar te /
NK092(khe)001:19410: rgyud tha dad kyi dbang du ru tra can dang /
NK092(khe)001:19411: rgyud gcig pa'i dbang du nga rgyal gyis dregs pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19417: sred meda dang bde ba spong ba /
NK092(khe)001:19419: stobsa ldan dang las kyi bag chags brtas pa /
NK092(khe)001:19420: spre'u dang rnam shes sam brag la gnas pa'i the'u rang dang yang mthun gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19421: ra dang 'du shes dmyal ba'i khyi lu 'de dang gzung 'dzin /
NK092(khe)001:19422: sbrang ma dang 'du byed dam gcig tu 'dun zhing gdug pa che bas bgegs dang yang mthun gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19423: bya roga dang tshor ba'am sha tshor bas gshin rje dang yang 'dra gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19424: srin bu me khyer dang dbang po /
NK092(khe)001:19425: 'khora ba'i sems can las ngan phal pa dang yul /
NK092(khe)001:19426: kun 'dus kyi mchan rnying las 'khor ba 'di nyid gza' dang rgyu skar du'ang gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19427: chu la gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang chu'i rtog pa /
NK092(khe)001:19428: sa la gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang sa'i rtogs pa /
NK092(khe)001:19429: nam mkha'a la gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang nam mkha'i rtog pa /
NK092(khe)001:19430: me la gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang me'i rtog pa /
NK092(khe)001:19432: kun 'dus kyi mchan las 'brug gi sgrar yang gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19433: bsam ngan gyi log sred can dang /
NK092(khe)001:19434: sems kyi rtog dpyod la sogas pa zhes dngos po
NK092(khe)001:19435: gzhan bsdu ba ni mu stegs byed la sogs pa
NK092(khe)001:19436: thams cad skal ba med pas bsgrad pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19437: mtshan mara 'dzin pa tha dad pa mtha' dag mi
NK092(khe)001:19438: gnas par ngo bo dag pas chos nyid mnyam pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19439: ngang du zug rngu dang bral te zhi bar gyur
NK092(khe)001:19444: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19445: de nas 'od zer de daga snod ldan byin gyis
NK092(khe)001:19446: rlobs pa'i phyir 'od gcig tu gyur nas nam mkha'a
NK092(khe)001:19448: 'khora manga po de daga shina tu skrag cing sngangs
NK092(khe)001:19449: te dbang dang rgyud kyi snod du rung bar gsola
NK092(khe)001:19450: ba btab pa / 'od kyis skal ngan bskrad pa la e ma'o /
NK092(khe)001:19452: skal ldan rnams rgyud sbyangs pa la e ma zhes ngam ste /
NK092(khe)001:19453: 'khor badga caga rnams la ston pa bcoma ldan 'adsa
NK092(khe)001:19454: kyis zab mo'i dbang bskur te gsang sngags kyi snod
NK092(khe)001:19455: du runga bar byin gyis brlab tu gsola /
NK092(khe)001:19456: thega pa chen po'i rigas su nges te mi 'gyur
NK092(khe)001:19457: bar gzung bar mdzad du gsola zhes gsola ba btab
NK092(khe)001:19458: pa lasa / 'di la dbang bskur ba dang rgyud kyi 'bru bshad pa gnyis su sbyar te /
NK092(khe)001:19459: phyi ltar na ston pas gnang ste rgyud kyi snod du rung bar byin gyi brlab pa ni /
NK092(khe)001:19460: bcoma ldan 'adsa kyis zhala gyi madngas las 'od dngos su phyung basa /
NK092(khe)001:19461: 'od zera de daga ye shesa kyi 'od du shar
NK092(khe)001:19462: te nyon mongs dang mtshan rtog zhi zhing chos nyid
NK092(khe)001:19463: kyi dbyings su 'khyil ba dang dbyings dang ye shes
NK092(khe)001:19464: gnyis med du gyur pas mdzesa shinga legs par thabs
NK092(khe)001:19465: kyi mchog gi bde basa gsang ba'i don gyi nyams
NK092(khe)001:19466: rnyed pa la dgod pa'i yon tan can des 'khor
NK092(khe)001:19467: thamsa cad kyi rgyud dag par mdzad de bsam pa
NK092(khe)001:19469: snod rnam para sbyangsa shing rgyud la yod pa'i rtog pa rnams bsal te /
NK092(khe)001:19470: slar 'od kyi gnas ston pa'i ljags su thim para gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:19472: bcoma ldana 'adsa yab yum gyis thabs shes rab rol
NK092(khe)001:19473: pa'i thig le gzi mdangs can bde ba'i ro dang
NK092(khe)001:19474: mtshung par ldan pa ston pa'i ngo bo de rdo
NK092(khe)001:19475: rje'i zhal gyi madngas las phyungsa pasa /
NK092(khe)001:19476: thig le'i 'od zera de daga rdo rje'i ye shes
NK092(khe)001:19477: kyi ngang du 'dus pa'i gnyis med kyi 'od mang
NK092(khe)001:19478: por rtog tshogs kun zhi zhing gcig tu 'dres te
NK092(khe)001:19479: 'khyil ba dang / rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK092(khe)001:19480: shes 'od gsal bas mdzesa shinga bde ba chen po'i
NK092(khe)001:19481: ros gang basa 'khor thamsa cad rang rang so so'i
NK092(khe)001:19482: rig pa dga' ba de'i ro can du gyur pas
NK092(khe)001:19484: bde ba'i nyams rnyed de dgyes pa'i ros tshim nas
NK092(khe)001:19485: snod kyi rgyud la yod pa'i rtog pa rnams rnam
NK092(khe)001:19486: para sbyangsa te / thig le drangs nas slar 'oda
NK092(khe)001:19487: kyi gnas su bzlog pas rang rang gi gnas tha
NK092(khe)001:19489: bum pa chus gang ba ltar bde ba'i ro dang bcas pas lus gang bar gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:19490: de ltar ye shes rang gnas bden pa'i tshig gis dbang bskur te zab mo'i snod du gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:19495: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19496: de nas rigs kyi bdag po phyag na rdo rje
NK092(khe)001:19497: la sogs pa'i 'khor dbang thob pa la rgyud bshad
NK092(khe)001:19498: pa nyid / gsang ba pas langa ka'i badga po
NK092(khe)001:19499: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas lo rgyus su
NK092(khe)001:19500: pa nyid / brjod pa ni / de nas ston
NK092(khe)001:19501: pa chen po bcom ldan 'adsa gasnga ba mchoga gi
NK092(khe)001:19502: badga pa de yi thugs mtshan nyid thams cad dang
NK092(khe)001:19503: bral ba'i mi gansa pa'i ye shes chena po'i dbyings
NK092(khe)001:19504: pa nyid / brjod pa ni / kyi klong nas
NK092(khe)001:19505: / sku mngon du snang bar ngesa para bzhengsa par
NK092(khe)001:19506: mdzad nas thams cad zil gyis gnod pas senga ge
NK092(khe)001:19507: rnam para rgyal ba'i sgra lta bus gsung gis bka'
NK092(khe)001:19508: stsal pa'i don gang zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:19510: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba ji bzhin pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19511: ye shes chen po la bsgrub bya dang shes bya'i
NK092(khe)001:19512: dona gyi snying po ji snyed pa ma btsal lhun
NK092(khe)001:19513: gyis grub par rdzogs pas bkod pa phun sum tshogs
NK092(khe)001:19514: pa de nyid ma sbas ma gab bar 'dogs su
NK092(khe)001:19515: gnang ba'i sgo nas tshig dang yi ger bstan pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19516: gzugs brnyan 'di yang de bzhin no //
NK092(khe)001:19517: mdzad pa ril lhun gyis grub pa'i byang chub kyi
NK092(khe)001:19518: sems de nyid gdul bya la rtagsa kyi rola par
NK092(khe)001:19519: rang snang ba'i zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK092(khe)001:19520: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du snang nas ji ltar 'dul ba'i don mdzad pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19521: dam pa rnams kyi gasnga ba'i mdzod gsum gyi nang
NK092(khe)001:19522: nas yang ngesa don dam pa yin pa'i phyir dang
NK092(khe)001:19523: / rgyud lung man ngag gi bka'a yi gnas kun
NK092(khe)001:19524: gtan la 'bebs pa'i 'grel pa yin pa'i phyir dang
NK092(khe)001:19525: / / chos rnams kyi ji lta ba nyid gsal
NK092(khe)001:19526: bar ston pa'i don du me longa gi gzugs brnyan
NK092(khe)001:19527: ltar ji bzhin du ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK092(khe)001:19528: / / pa'i phyir dang / chos rtags kyi gtan
NK092(khe)001:19529: tshigas bzhi dang sgo gsum gyi lde'u mig gsum po
NK092(khe)001:19530: thams cad gsal bar 'byung ba'i gansa su gyur pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19531: / / pa'i phyir dang / phyir dang / rgyal
NK092(khe)001:19532: ba ril gyi dgongsa pa thams cad kyi don gyi
NK092(khe)001:19534: ji bzhin pa'i gsang ba nyid mi phyed pas rdo
NK092(khe)001:19535: rje rang byung 'dus ma byas pa la yon tan
NK092(khe)001:19536: dang 'bras bu thams cad ma brtsal bar rdzogs pas
NK092(khe)001:19537: rnam para bsgyingsa te brjid pa'i rgyud dang /
NK092(khe)001:19538: theg pa'i lugs kyi gzhung dam pa rnams ma 'khyar
NK092(khe)001:19539: ba'i don chena po theg pa'i rgyal po'i rtsa ba
NK092(khe)001:19540: nyid bshad pa'i sgra yi gsang ba 'di byung ngo
NK092(khe)001:19542: bshad pa'i mtshan dang che ba ji ltar bstan kyang
NK092(khe)001:19543: yi ge gsum bshad pa gzhan dkyil 'khor rnam gsum
NK092(khe)001:19544: gyi don gyi ngo bo brdas bstan pa der 'dus
NK092(khe)001:19545: pas yi ge'i don gsum gyi mtshan brgyad du yon
NK092(khe)001:19546: tan gyi khyad par gyis bsgrangs pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19547: 'on kyang mdo de dag tsam brjod pas gsang bdag
NK092(khe)001:19548: la sogs pa'i sgrib pa mtha' spangs kyi 'khor rtsal
NK092(khe)001:19549: chen pa rnams kyis rgyas par go bar 'gyur ro
NK092(khe)001:19551: +amo yab m+aum yum h'u gnyis su med pa'i sgo
NK092(khe)001:19552: nas ye shes chen po gsang ba mchog gi rgyud
NK092(khe)001:19554: dngos su brjod pa ni ma yin no //
NK092(khe)001:19555: de yang ston pasa ngo bo nyid kyi ngang las tshig canga mi gsung zhing /
NK092(khe)001:19556: chos sku'i klong nas rab tu mi gsung ste /
NK092(khe)001:19557: gsung ba'i rtsol rtog mi mnga' ba'i phyir ro //
NK092(khe)001:19558: longs sku'i dgongs pa bden pa res mos bral bas
NK092(khe)001:19559: mi g.yo ba chen po la gdul bya'i ngor bstan
NK092(khe)001:19560: pa'i don bka' stsal ba'i gsunga pa mi 'goga la
NK092(khe)001:19561: / sprul sku'i brjod pa tshig gi gsung 'goga pa
NK092(khe)001:19562: ma yina te ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du bka'
NK092(khe)001:19564: de ltar ched du ma gsungas te gsungs pa mi
NK092(khe)001:19565: mnga' ba nyid na'ang bsam gyis mi khyab par rgya
NK092(khe)001:19566: chera bashada pa'i ngo bora gang la'ang mi gnas par
NK092(khe)001:19571: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19573: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK092(khe)001:19574: bshad pa de daga ni rtsa ba gleng slong ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19575: sbyor ba bstan pa 'byung ba'i yan lag ces bya'o
NK092(khe)001:19576: // zhes gleng bslang ba'i ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19578: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chena po lasa /
NK092(khe)001:19579: rtsa ba sbyor ba'i yan lag gleng bslang ba'i tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK092(khe)001:19580: bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad pa nyid rnam par bshad pa'o
NK092(khe)001:19581: ////gsum pa 'brel ba'i yan lag bshad pa la gsum
NK092(khe)001:19589: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19590: le'u 'dis nges don dang drang don gnyis ka ston no //
NK092(khe)001:19591: de nas ston pa gsang bdag chen pos /
NK092(khe)001:19592: yan lag gsum pa rgyas par bstan ba'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19594: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK092(khe)001:19595: de la bstan pa 'byung ba'i dgos pa dang 'brel ba'i yan lag ganga zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:19596: ganga rgyu dang thabs kyi dngos gzhi dang /
NK092(khe)001:19597: ganga 'bras bu dang thabs las byung ba'i dngos po
NK092(khe)001:19598: rnams med na mi 'byung bar nges te 'brel zhing
NK092(khe)001:19599: rjod byed dang brjod bya yang de ltar rtag tu
NK092(khe)001:19601: de yi don ni 'di ltar nye bar byung ba
NK092(khe)001:19602: gang yin pa sdud pa po khyod kyis go bar
NK092(khe)001:19603: bya ba'i dgos ched kyi don du ston pa ngas
NK092(khe)001:19604: rgyas par bgro ba cheda du brjod de bstan para
NK092(khe)001:19605: bya'o // zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19612: thabs dang thabs byung gi 'brel ba bshad pa /
NK092(khe)001:19613: rgyu dang 'bras bur 'brel ba bstan pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19615: ston pas rdo rje sems dpa' la shod cig par bskul ba /
NK092(khe)001:19616: sems dpa' rdo rjes 'chad pa'i dbang zhus pa /
NK092(khe)001:19617: ston pas 'chad pa'i bka' sdod skyes bur dbang bskur ba /
NK092(khe)001:19618: thabs las byung ba dbang gi yon tan no //
NK092(khe)001:19622: bskul ba rnam par mdzad do //
NK092(khe)001:19623: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19624: dgos 'brel bzhi las rjod byed 'chad pa'i skyes bu nyid kyi don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19626: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK092(khe)001:19627: gleng bslang ba de nas mdun bsu ba lta bur /
NK092(khe)001:19628: gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin phyag na rdo rje badga nyid
NK092(khe)001:19629: la ston pas dbang bskur nas rgyud bshad pa'i dus
NK092(khe)001:19630: gnyis 'dzom pa de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK092(khe)001:19631: bdag gi mtshan dam tshiga chen po rdo rje semsa dapa'a zhes bya bar gyur pa la /
NK092(khe)001:19632: ston pa bcom ldan 'adsa rigs bdag kun tu bzang po gasnga ba mchoga gi badga po desa /
NK092(khe)001:19633: dgos pa gang gi phyir na /
NK092(khe)001:19634: gdul bya rnams 'bras bu'i go 'phang mchog la skyol
NK092(khe)001:19635: bas thega pa chena po dngos po'i gnas lugs ji
NK092(khe)001:19636: bzhin par ston pas gasnga ba'i don bla na med
NK092(khe)001:19637: pa nyid 'khor gzhan la phyag na rdo rje badga
NK092(khe)001:19638: nyid kyis rig pa khyad par can la dgongs pa
NK092(khe)001:19639: brda'i sgo nas rgya chera ched du brjod pa dang
NK092(khe)001:19640: go phye ba'i 'khor la gsung du bsgrags nas 'chad
NK092(khe)001:19641: cing cheda du brjod ciga para mnga' gsol nas ston
NK092(khe)001:19642: du gzhug par dgongas pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19644: gzhan rnam par bcad de ston pas sems dpa' rdo
NK092(khe)001:19645: rje badga nyid kho na la nyi tshera zhala 'dud
NK092(khe)001:19646: para spyan gyis gzigsa te 'dzum pa mdzad pasa gsang
NK092(khe)001:19647: ba mchog gi lung chen bshad pa'i bskul ba rnam
NK092(khe)001:19648: para mdzad do // 'di nyid shugs la ston pas gleng bslang bar yang 'agro'o //
NK092(khe)001:19652: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19653: de nasa dus der badga gi mtshan dam tshiga chen
NK092(khe)001:19654: po rdo rje semsa dapa'a zhesa bya bar grags shing
NK092(khe)001:19655: sdud pa por snang ba desa /
NK092(khe)001:19656: ston pas brda'i sgo nas rgyud 'chad par yang dag para bskul bar rnam para riga cing shes nasa /
NK092(khe)001:19657: ston pa la 'chad pa'i dbang nod pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19658: bdag sems dpa' rdo rje ranga gi stan lasa langsa te /
NK092(khe)001:19659: ranga gi thugs mtshon pa'i rtags kyi matshana ma rdo
NK092(khe)001:19660: rje rgya gram de yis bdag nyid kyi spyi bo
NK092(khe)001:19661: la sogs ba gansa lngar riga para byas nasa /
NK092(khe)001:19662: gsang sngags thega pa chena po'i don gyi de kho
NK092(khe)001:19663: na nyid ma nor bar rgya chera brjod para bya
NK092(khe)001:19664: ba'i cheda du / ngag rdo rjer byin gyis brlab
NK092(khe)001:19665: cing khyad par du yang bdag gi lce nyes pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19666: skyon gyis ma gos par 'chad pa'i rtags chu skyes
NK092(khe)001:19667: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i steng du rdo rje
NK092(khe)001:19669: sgo gsum shina tu gus pa'i tshul gyis lus kyi
NK092(khe)001:19670: baga bzhi dang lto ba sa la phaba pa'i brkyang
NK092(khe)001:19671: phyag rnal 'byor gyi theg pa gsang chen nang pa'i
NK092(khe)001:19673: bag tsha ba dang 'jigs pa med pas seng ge'i
NK092(khe)001:19674: lta stangsa kyis ston pa'i zhal du bltas te 'di
NK092(khe)001:19676: rdo rje gsum mi phyed pa'i mnga' bdag mtha' kun
NK092(khe)001:19677: las rgyal ba'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi ngo bo
NK092(khe)001:19678: 'khor 'dus pa'i tshogas kyi gtso badga chen po nyid
NK092(khe)001:19679: bdag la thugs brtse bas dgongsa su gsola /
NK092(khe)001:19680: ston pa chosa kyi rgyal po dgongs pa mi g.yo
NK092(khe)001:19681: zhing bskyod pa med pas brjid pa ched du bsgrub
NK092(khe)001:19682: pa med par rje rgyal mchog gi tshul lugs su
NK092(khe)001:19684: rgyal mchoga kun tu bzang po bde ba chena po'i
NK092(khe)001:19685: longs spyod la rol ba'i sa mchog khyab gdal lhun
NK092(khe)001:19686: rdzogs la raba tu bzhugs te ci yang mi gsung
NK092(khe)001:19687: la / 'on kyang sems dpa' rdo rje bdag ni
NK092(khe)001:19688: chos smra ba'i lasa chen gsang sngags ston pa mchoga
NK092(khe)001:19690: rdo rje lta bu'i lce 'od du 'abra basa cir yang sgrogs te don mtshon pa 'di nyid /
NK092(khe)001:19691: gsung chos kyi sgra dbyangas kyi mnga' bdag phyogs bcu
NK092(khe)001:19692: dus bzhi'i rgyal ba rigs kyi bdag po rnams kyis
NK092(khe)001:19693: byin gyis brlab ste badga 'chad pa'i mthu dang ldan
NK092(khe)001:19694: par byin gyis rlobsa par gyis shig ces gsol ba
NK092(khe)001:19695: btab pa dang / gsang sngags thams cad kyi'ang rgyal
NK092(khe)001:19696: po rgyud mchog thun mong ma yin pa mdo chen
NK092(khe)001:19697: po chos kyi me longa 'di nyid /
NK092(khe)001:19698: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yang rab mchoga
NK092(khe)001:19699: dbang phyug chen po chosa kyi rgyal po nyid kyi
NK092(khe)001:19700: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs kyi mthus /
NK092(khe)001:19701: bdag gis 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogas rnams la rgya cher brjod para 'osa pas bshad par rigs so //
NK092(khe)001:19703: a ho zhes dgyes bskyed pa'i sgra dang bcas par zhus pas gsola ba btab pa lasa /
NK092(khe)001:19707: lag tu babs par gyur nas /
NK092(khe)001:19708: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19709: de nas ston pa kun tu bzang po gasnga ba mchoga gi mnga' badga chen po desa /
NK092(khe)001:19710: badga gasnga ba 'dzin pa nyid gsang chen rdo rje
NK092(khe)001:19711: theg pa yang dag bar 'chad pa'i lasa byed kyi
NK092(khe)001:19712: skyes bur las gnyer gtad de bka'a sdod dam para
NK092(khe)001:19713: bsgo ba de / gsang sngags rdo rje rgyal po'i
NK092(khe)001:19714: theg pa rgya cher smra zhing brjod pa chen pora
NK092(khe)001:19715: byin gyis brlab nas stobs dang ldan par bya ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19716: bsgo ba de / phyir / ston pa nyid rdo
NK092(khe)001:19717: rje gsum dbyer med pa'i ngang las gsang sngags kyi
NK092(khe)001:19718: bstan pa zab mo rnam para 'phro zhing 'byung ba
NK092(khe)001:19719: zhesa bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dgongas pa la
NK092(khe)001:19720: snyomsa para zhugsa nas ljagsa kyi 'od zer las /
NK092(khe)001:19721: badz+ra karma sa t+wa tsa kra ha ha ham /
NK092(khe)001:19724: rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'khor lo 'od 'bar ba zhig byung /
NK092(khe)001:19726: de'ang sa t+wa'i sgra las sems dapa'a'am brtan pa ste /
NK092(khe)001:19727: rdo rje gsum mi phyed par brtan pas phrin las
NK092(khe)001:19728: kyi sems dpa' chen por byin gyis rlobs pas dbang
NK092(khe)001:19729: gi rdzas rdo rje rgya grama gyi 'khor lo 'od
NK092(khe)001:19731: semsa dapa'a rdo rje kho na badga nyid du gyur
NK092(khe)001:19732: pa de'i lag tu nges par babsa para gyur nasa
NK092(khe)001:19733: 'chad pa'i dbang thab pas ston pa dang skyes bu
NK092(khe)001:19734: thabs dang thabs byung gi tshul du 'brel ba'o //
NK092(khe)001:19735: 'di la kun 'dus kyi 'chad tshul gcig la /
NK092(khe)001:19736: snga nas phyag mtshan du rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig bsnams pa la /
NK092(khe)001:19737: phyis rdo rjes dbang bskur ba gnyis lte ba bsnol
NK092(khe)001:19738: bas rdo rje rgya gram du gyur par 'chad pa
NK092(khe)001:19741: chos 'chad pa'i nus pa dang ldan par gyur pa /
NK092(khe)001:19742: 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i don byed tshul lo //
NK092(khe)001:19746: ldan pa chen por gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:19747: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19748: de ltar thabs las byung ba 'chad pa'i lasa byed
NK092(khe)001:19749: pa nyid kyi rdo rje'i dabnga bskur ba thoba ste
NK092(khe)001:19750: / bdag gis kyang dbang thob pa'i rtags dang yon tan /
NK092(khe)001:19751: rgya che ba gsang sngags kyi chos kyi rnam grangs
NK092(khe)001:19752: sna tshogs pa so so'i bye brag ma 'dres par
NK092(khe)001:19753: ston pa'i rnam para smra ba cheen pora gyur nas
NK092(khe)001:19754: / lung chen gsang ba'i rgyud 'di'i don thogs pa
NK092(khe)001:19755: med par 'chad pa'i shina tu bla bkyal ba'i spobsa
NK092(khe)001:19756: pa can du byin gyisa brlabs par mdzad pas gsang
NK092(khe)001:19757: sngags kyi bdag por gyur nas /
NK092(khe)001:19758: dus thams cad nas thams cad kun tu bdag gi
NK092(khe)001:19759: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ched du bsdams pa med
NK092(khe)001:19760: par mi gzoba pa 'dra bar snang yang /
NK092(khe)001:19761: ngo bo logs par gyur te 'khrul pa mi 'byung
NK092(khe)001:19762: bar raba tu baga dang ldan pa cheena pora gyur
NK092(khe)001:19763: to // de ltar dbang thob pa ni dgos 'brel
NK092(khe)001:19764: bzhi las thabs dang thabs byung gi 'brel ba'i tshul
NK092(khe)001:19768: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19769: de nasa 'chad pa'i nus pa dang ldan par gyur pa'i badga rdo rje semsa dapa'a des /
NK092(khe)001:19770: dbang thob pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis 'khor
NK092(khe)001:19771: rnams spro ba bskyed de zhing khams dag pa chen
NK092(khe)001:19772: por byin gyis rlobs pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19773: 'chad pa'i phrin lasa kyi matshana ma rdo rje rgya gram de nyid lag tu blangsa nas /
NK092(khe)001:19775: rdo rje theg pa'i dam pa'i chos brda tshiga sna
NK092(khe)001:19776: tshogas dang bshad thabs mang po nyid kyis sku gsung
NK092(khe)001:19777: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19778: chos kyi 'khor lo lana grangsa lnga lngar bskyar zhing bskor ro //
NK092(khe)001:19779: rnam pa bcu gnyis ni nyi shu ste /
NK092(khe)001:19780: de ltar nyi shu rtsa lngar bskor ba ni lan grangs te /
NK092(khe)001:19781: don gyi gzhi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK092(khe)001:19782: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i phyir grangs thun mong du bstan
NK092(khe)001:19784: yang na lnga pa lnga las /
NK092(khe)001:19785: dang po chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i gtan tshigs lnga /
NK092(khe)001:19786: gnyis pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga /
NK092(khe)001:19791: chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan las /
NK092(khe)001:19792: sku rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor la sogs pa lnga /
NK092(khe)001:19793: de las 'phros pa rnams kyang gsung /
NK092(khe)001:19795: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid kyi dbang du na /
NK092(khe)001:19797: rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga'i chos bstan pa ste /
NK092(khe)001:19798: de nyid yan lags bcu dang rnal 'byor bcu ste
NK092(khe)001:19799: rnam pa bcu phrag gnyis su chos kyi 'khor lo
NK092(khe)001:19801: bsdoms pas nyi shu rtsa lngar gyur pa la /
NK092(khe)001:19802: re re la'ang bye brag gi dbye bas grangsa bcu
NK092(khe)001:19803: phrag gnyis dang lngar bsgyur te rmad du byung ba'i
NK092(khe)001:19804: chos bstan pasa zhing thams cad kyi gzhi lnga las
NK092(khe)001:19805: snang ba'i 'khor mang po rnams la rang rang gi
NK092(khe)001:19806: thabs dang 'tshams pa'i chos su snang zhing /
NK092(khe)001:19808: rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'khor lo bskor bas rtse
NK092(khe)001:19809: mo nyi shu las 'od zer gyi d+r+wa ba nyi
NK092(khe)001:19810: shus 'gro ba lnga'i don byas pa la'ang gsungs so
NK092(khe)001:19811: // de ltar thun mong ma yin pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas /
NK092(khe)001:19812: phyi nang gnyis kyi tshul du zhing khamsa mtha' dag thams cad rnam para g.yos te /
NK092(khe)001:19816: kun tu raba tu g.yos te g.yo ba tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19818: rig pa la gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor g.yos te
NK092(khe)001:19819: rtsa ba lnga'i don ldang ba dang g.yo tshabs che
NK092(khe)001:19821: 'dun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor la gnyis las dang po'i sems gong du g.yo ba'am /
NK092(khe)001:19822: dang po 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa thob par yang gsungs la /
NK092(khe)001:19826: kun tu raba tu 'gul te 'gul tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19827: rig pa don gyi phyogs su bskyod pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19828: gnyis pa'i dus kyi sems gong du bskyod pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19829: gnyis pa rten pa gzhi yi sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19830: ldeg /raba tu ldeg /kun tu raba tu ldeg ste /
NK092(khe)001:19831: ldeg tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19832: logs su gyur pas rang gi sa la mi rten pas sa gong mar 'gro ba'am /
NK092(khe)001:19833: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor sbyor ba'i dus kyi sems gong mar 'gro ba'am /
NK092(khe)001:19834: gsum pa gal chen sbyong ba'i sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19838: 'khrugs tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19839: sa go nga ma'i yang gong ma'i don rig pa dang mi phyed par gyur pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19840: dbugs chen 'byin pa'i dus su gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba mi gnas pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19841: bzhi pa bslab pa rgyun gyis thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19845: 'ur tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19846: rnam par rtog pa skabs kyi sgrib pa rnams 'phyag pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19848: lung bstan gyi sgra snyan pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19849: lnga pa bsod nams gter gyi sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19852: kun tu raba tu chema ste /
NK092(khe)001:19853: chem tshabs che chung gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19854: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags kyi sgrib pa thams cad 'joms pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19855: rnal 'byor lnga mthar phyin te rtsal chen rdzogs par gyur pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19856: drug pa rten pas khyad par du 'gro ba'i sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19859: dbus mtho na mtha'a dam'a ba ni /
NK092(khe)001:19860: nang ltar na rtogs pa shar ba'i ltas te /
NK092(khe)001:19861: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las rdzogs pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19862: bdun pa dmigs pas 'bras bu skye ba'i sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19864: shara mtho na ni nub dam'a /
NK092(khe)001:19865: nub mtho na ni shar dam'a ba ni /
NK092(khe)001:19867: zhi ba dang dbang gi phrin las grub pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19868: rgyad pa gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa thob pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19871: byang mtho na lho dma' bar gyur pa ni /
NK092(khe)001:19872: rgyas pa dang drag po'i phrin las grub pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:19873: dgu pa gdal ba chos nyid kyi sa mchog thob nas sa'i rim pa mthar phyin te /
NK092(khe)001:19874: bcu pa rdzogs pa spyi chibs kyi sa dam pa mngon du byas pas /
NK092(khe)001:19875: zhing khamas thamsa cad kyi gdul zhing gi 'khor rnams
NK092(khe)001:19876: gsang sngags thos shing gsang don rtogs pas badga gsang
NK092(khe)001:19877: ba'i bdag po rdo rje semsa dapa'a dang 'dra ba
NK092(khe)001:19878: sha stag lta bura gyur nas /
NK092(khe)001:19879: de dag kun kyang gsang sngags kyi theg pa'i don
NK092(khe)001:19880: gyi snying po ngo bo nyid nor ba med par
NK092(khe)001:19881: phyin ci ma loga pa'i tshul gyis rgya chera brjod
NK092(khe)001:19882: cing ston pa'i sgra rnam para brjod de smra bar
NK092(khe)001:19884: badga 'chad pa'i skyes bu semsa dapa'a rdo rje nyid
NK092(khe)001:19885: kyang rgyal tshab tu gnang ba thob nas rnam para
NK092(khe)001:19886: brjid cing shin tu rngoma pa'i rnam rol du bkod
NK092(khe)001:19887: de bstan pa mchog gi chos 'chad par 'khor rnams
NK092(khe)001:19889: rigs kyi bdag po ston pa'i mdun logas su senga
NK092(khe)001:19890: ge'i khri rdo rjesa matshana pas brgyan pa'i chos 'chad
NK092(khe)001:19891: pa'i khri la / lus 'gying baga gi tshul gyis 'jug cing rnam para gnas so //
NK092(khe)001:19892: gong gi phyi'i ltas rnams kyang gdul bya'i ngo la
NK092(khe)001:19893: phyi rol gyi cho 'phrul sna tshogs su snang bar
NK092(khe)001:19894: shes par bya'o // 'o na le'u bcu bdun pa'i stod dang /
NK092(khe)001:19896: 'di gsum bldabs so zhes brgal na /
NK092(khe)001:19897: dang po ni chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul dang yig 'bru rnams kyi byin rlabs kyis yin la /
NK092(khe)001:19898: gnyis pa ni ru tras 'bras bu thob pa'i tshe de'i mthus yin cing /
NK092(khe)001:19899: 'dir ni sdud pa po la dbang bskur bas 'chad
NK092(khe)001:19900: pa'i skyes bur gyur pa'i byin rlabs kyis yin pas
NK092(khe)001:19902: de bas na phyag na rdo rjes rigs kyi bdag po gcig la'ang thos la /
NK092(khe)001:19903: 'dir 'chad pa po yin pa'ang lo rgyus 'dis the tshom med par gsal lo //
NK092(khe)001:19905: 'brel ba dang ldan par bstod pa /
NK092(khe)001:19908: de las byung ba'i yon tan dang ldan par 'khor gyis bstod pa /
NK092(khe)001:19909: ston pa mchog gis bstod pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:19913: kho bo la bstod pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19914: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19915: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel ba gang snyam pa la /
NK092(khe)001:19916: 'chad pa'i skyes bus chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ma thag pa de nas /
NK092(khe)001:19917: lang ka'i la sogs pa 'dus pa'i tshogas kyi 'khor yongs su rdzogs pa phala mo che rnams kyis /
NK092(khe)001:19918: sems dpa' rdo rje la ngo mtshar skyes nas bcoma ldana 'adsa la 'di skad cesa gsola to //
NK092(khe)001:19919: 'chad pa'i skyes bu la ngam nas /
NK092(khe)001:19922: ston pa bcoma ldan 'adsa la bos nas /
NK092(khe)001:19923: 'chad pa'i skyes bu semsa dapa'a rdo rje zhes bya
NK092(khe)001:19924: ba 'di ni rgyud kyi don gting phyin par rtogs
NK092(khe)001:19925: pa dang / 'gro don mdzad pa'i thabs khyad par can mnga' bas /
NK092(khe)001:19926: thabs dang shes rab kyi gdul dka' drag po kun btul bas 'di ltar mathu che ba /
NK092(khe)001:19927: zhing khams thams cad kyi sa g.yos pa sogs su gyur pas 'di ltar byin rlabsa che ba /
NK092(khe)001:19928: ma 'dres pa'i chos kun mkhyen pas ye shes thams
NK092(khe)001:19929: cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur te thabs kyi gsang
NK092(khe)001:19930: mdzod mnga' bas 'di ltar rgya che ba /
NK092(khe)001:19931: dgongs don thams cad kyi mdzod du gyur te chos
NK092(khe)001:19932: nyid yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pas 'di ltar 'chad
NK092(khe)001:19934: dgongs pa'i lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin ma 'dres
NK092(khe)001:19935: yongs rdzogs su shar bas 'di ltar gasla zhing zaba
NK092(khe)001:19936: pa yi yon tan dang ldan pa'i 'chad ba'i skyes
NK092(khe)001:19938: bcoma ldan 'adsa khyod kyi thugs dang rgyu 'bras su
NK092(khe)001:19939: 'brel zhing thugas kyi byin rlabs lasa skyes te snang
NK092(khe)001:19940: ba / gsang sngags ji bzhin pa ston pa'i rang
NK092(khe)001:19941: bzhin de kho na nyid dang ngo bo bdag nyid
NK092(khe)001:19943: de kho na nyid de'i byin rlabs lasa skyes te snang ba lagas so //
NK092(khe)001:19945: ston pa'i spyan sngar kho bo gsang bdag nyid la bstod pa dang /
NK092(khe)001:19949: brjod pa bka' stsal pa las /
NK092(khe)001:19950: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:19953: ston pa chen po bcoma ldan 'adsa desa /
NK092(khe)001:19954: 'khor de daga la dwang ba skyed pa'i phyir 'chad
NK092(khe)001:19955: pa'i skyes bu'i yon tan bka'a stsal te bshad pa
NK092(khe)001:19958: yon tan gyi rnam grangs bcu gnyis po 'di dag chos can dang /
NK092(khe)001:19960: gtan tshigs kyi tshul gyis stoon te /
NK092(khe)001:19961: rgyal tshab 'chad pa'i skyes bu semsa dapa'a rdo rje 'di ni /
NK092(khe)001:19962: zhes pa chos can du byas nas /
NK092(khe)001:19963: byang chub semsa kyi ngo bo yin te zhes dam bca' ba dang /
NK092(khe)001:19965: snying rje thams cad kyi badga po /
NK092(khe)001:19966: thabsa thamsa cad kyi mchoga /sangsa rgyas thamsa cad kyi rje btsun /
NK092(khe)001:19967: byang chub semsa dapa'a thams cad kyi yaba /
NK092(khe)001:19969: mya ngana lasa 'adsa pa kun gyi deda dpona /
NK092(khe)001:19970: bdud thams cad kyi yanga bdud chena po /
NK092(khe)001:19971: sangsa rgyas thamsa cada kyi yanga gdul daka'a 'dul ba /
NK092(khe)001:19973: gasnga ba thamsa cada kyi badga po /
NK092(khe)001:19974: ye shes thamsa cad kyi 'byung gansa chena pora gyur pa yina no //
NK092(khe)001:19975: zhes dam bca' bcu gnyis so //
NK092(khe)001:19976: de dag gi gtan tshigs phyogs phyi mas byas nas nges par 'grel te /
NK092(khe)001:19978: zhes de dag gtan tshigs gang gis mngon na 'di lta ste /
NK092(khe)001:19979: thoga ma dang tha ma meda para mnyam pa'i dus kyi ngo bor gnas pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19981: 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med pa'i dus
NK092(khe)001:19982: nyid nas rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems rtsol
NK092(khe)001:19983: mthas ma bsgos shing ril gyi dngos gzhi g.yo ba
NK092(khe)001:19984: dang bral ba la gnyis pa'i chos thams cad ma
NK092(khe)001:19985: dmigs par chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngo bo /
NK092(khe)001:19986: dus gsum ma 'gag la bral bas mtshan nyid thams cad pa'i phyir zhes dang po'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:19987: pha mtha'a las kyang pha mtha'a yas pa'i snying rje'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19989: dus thog ma'i pha mtha' las kyang thog ma'i pha
NK092(khe)001:19990: mtha' tshad med pa nas thugs rje chen po ril
NK092(khe)001:19991: 'byung ba'i dbang phyug chen po yin pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19992: zhes gnyis pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:19993: dapaga tu meda cing bsam du med pa mnga' ba'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:19995: thabs kyi bye brag mang po dpag tu med cing
NK092(khe)001:19996: ngo bo bsam du med pas zab pa sna tshogs
NK092(khe)001:19997: che ba dang yangs pa mnga' bas gong na med
NK092(khe)001:19998: pa'i phyir / zhes gsum pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:19999: 'byamsa klas pa'i dus nas lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20001: mu mtha' med cing 'byams klas pa'i dus nas mnyam
NK092(khe)001:20002: pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid dam
NK092(khe)001:20004: zhes bzhi pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:20005: bya ba byas shinga byed pa byas pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20007: bdag gi don gyi bya ba lhun gyis rdzogs par byas shing /
NK092(khe)001:20008: gzhan sa la gnas pa'i sems dpa' chen po rnams
NK092(khe)001:20009: kyi don byed pa yang ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin
NK092(khe)001:20010: du mdzad cing byas te 'bras bu'i sa la 'don
NK092(khe)001:20011: pa'i phyir / zhes lnga pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:20012: mngona para rdzogsa para sangsa rgyas pa yina pa'i phyir te /
NK092(khe)001:20014: gsang sngags snying po'i de bzhin nyid chen po'i rig
NK092(khe)001:20015: pa mngon du byas pas skyed du bya ba med
NK092(khe)001:20016: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de la /
NK092(khe)001:20017: mtha' dang zhen mtha' med par rnal ma'i don la
NK092(khe)001:20018: 'byor pas mi g.yo gdal ba chen po'i dgongs par
NK092(khe)001:20019: bzhugs pa'i phyir / zhes drug pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:20020: de ni chosa thamsa cad kyi ranga bzhina du sbyor zhing go 'phang mchog la 'god pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20022: sems dpa' rdo rje de ni 'khor ba dang mya
NK092(khe)001:20023: ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK092(khe)001:20024: ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang du chos kun
NK092(khe)001:20025: yongs rdzogs su sbyor zhing gdul bya rnams kyang go
NK092(khe)001:20029: chosa thamsa cada kyi ranga bzhina du 'brel basa mi mthun phyogs kun 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20031: dngos po'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gzhi ji
NK092(khe)001:20032: bzhin pa'i de kho na nyid du son te bdag
NK092(khe)001:20033: nyid chen por 'brel bas ye shes chen pos bdud
NK092(khe)001:20034: bzhi'i dpung thams cad bcom pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20035: zhes brgyad pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:20036: rgyal ba thamsa cad kyi thugs lasa skyes shing stobs rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20038: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs ye
NK092(khe)001:20039: shes chen po'i byin rlabs las skyes shing byin rlabs
NK092(khe)001:20040: kun gyi bdag nyid du snang bas /
NK092(khe)001:20041: mthu thams cad kyi yang bdag por gyur te /
NK092(khe)001:20042: gnod sbyin la sogs pa shin tu nyon mongs che
NK092(khe)001:20043: zhing kha lo bsgyur bar dka' ba dag gi gnyen
NK092(khe)001:20045: zhes dgu pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK092(khe)001:20046: rgyal ba kun gyi thugsa dang 'brel ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20048: sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes kyi thugs dang rgyu
NK092(khe)001:20049: dang 'bras bur 'brel bas dgongs pa'i gsang don thams
NK092(khe)001:20050: cad bdag gi thob pas bstan pa ril dang gsang
NK092(khe)001:20051: sngags 'byung ba'i mdzod kyi gnas chen por gyur pa'i
NK092(khe)001:20052: phyir zhes bcu gcig pa dang bcu pa'i gtan tshigs
NK092(khe)001:20054: thamsa cada kyi yaba tu gyur pa yin pa'i phyir te /
NK092(khe)001:20056: rang byung gi ye shes ni gsang ba dam pa thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid pas /
NK092(khe)001:20057: ye shes ji snyed pa thams cad 'char zhing snang ba'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir te /
NK092(khe)001:20058: yon tan gyi khyad par phun sum tshogs pa de ni /
NK092(khe)001:20060: zhesa kho bo la basngagasa pa brjod de yon tan
NK092(khe)001:20061: ci yod pa thams cad mchog tu bka'a stsal pa
NK092(khe)001:20062: lasa ni / 'khor rnams gsang bdag la gsang don zhu ba la gzud pa'i ched do //
NK092(khe)001:20066: bshad du med pa'i khungs bstan pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20071: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20072: ston pas phyag na rdo rje la basngagasa pa'i yon tan brjod pa la /
NK092(khe)001:20073: 'dus pa'i tshogas kyi 'khor thamsa cad ngam zhing ngo mtshar du gyur te /
NK092(khe)001:20074: ngo mtshar ba'i ngo bo'i tshig bsnan nas smras te gsola pa /
NK092(khe)001:20076: de ltar thabs dang thabs las byung ba'i 'brel ba
NK092(khe)001:20077: 'di ni rang don gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin pas
NK092(khe)001:20079: bde bar gshegas pa de nyid de las byung bar
NK092(khe)001:20080: 'brel ba 'di ni gzhan don gyi phrin las mthar
NK092(khe)001:20081: phyin pas 'di ltar ngo matshara lagas so //
NK092(khe)001:20083: rgyud kyi don zhu ba'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20084: 'khor rnams kyis semsa dapa'a rdo rje dam pa gsang
NK092(khe)001:20085: bdag phyag na rdo rje de la ston pa chen
NK092(khe)001:20086: po'i spyan sngar ma yin par gud dam logas su
NK092(khe)001:20087: sgo gsum btud par byas nasa /
NK092(khe)001:20088: lusa kyi bag bzhi dang lto ba sa la phaba
NK092(khe)001:20089: pa'i brkyang phyag nang gi rnal 'byor gyi lugsa su
NK092(khe)001:20090: byas nasa / mnyes pas gnang ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20091: ye shes chen po rang snang ba'i rmada du byung ba'i me tog khyad par can dang /
NK092(khe)001:20092: phyi nang gsang ba'i ting nge 'dzina gyi mchod pa
NK092(khe)001:20093: mang po sna tshogas pa bsam pas sprul zhing mchod
NK092(khe)001:20095: ston pas dbang bskur zhing ji ltar gsungs pa 'di
NK092(khe)001:20096: ltar yon tan rmad du byung ba mnga' ba'i ngo
NK092(khe)001:20097: matshara chen po'i skyes bu sems dpa' rdo rje khyod
NK092(khe)001:20098: / rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kun tu bzang
NK092(khe)001:20099: po rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po'i thugs lasa rgyal
NK092(khe)001:20100: tshab 'chad pa'i skyes bur 'khrungs shing skyes pa tshul
NK092(khe)001:20101: ji ltar yang da ltar gyi zhing khams dam pa
NK092(khe)001:20102: 'dira skur snang nas ston par gyur zhiga gu ste
NK092(khe)001:20103: snang ba ngo mtshan bla na med pa khyod nyid
NK092(khe)001:20104: / / ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams bskyed
NK092(khe)001:20105: pa'i yab tu gyur cing ston pa kun tu bzang
NK092(khe)001:20106: po'i thugs las skyes pas rgyal ba'i sras /
NK092(khe)001:20107: chos thams cad kyi ranga bzhina de kho na nyid
NK092(khe)001:20108: dang gnyis su med par sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs
NK092(khe)001:20109: dang gciga tu 'brel ba'i 'chad pa po lags pas
NK092(khe)001:20110: / khyod kyis gsang sngags gsang ba mchog gi bka'a
NK092(khe)001:20111: yi lung chen rgyud sde zab mo'i chos kyi 'khor
NK092(khe)001:20112: lo rab tu bskor bar mdzad pasa /
NK092(khe)001:20113: log pa'i lam dang bral bas rnam par daga cing
NK092(khe)001:20114: thabs kyi nye lam mchoga tu gyur pa gsang sngags
NK092(khe)001:20115: gsang chen dam pa'i don mchog bla na med pa
NK092(khe)001:20116: daga / thun mong ma yin pa'i tshiga gisa gsal
NK092(khe)001:20117: bar mtshona te rgyud rgyal rgyud kyi snying po nyid
NK092(khe)001:20118: rnam par bshad de gsang don ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK092(khe)001:20119: su gsal bar mdzoda cig /zhes zhus te /
NK092(khe)001:20120: a ho zhes dgyes sgra dang bcas pas gsola ba btab bo //
NK092(khe)001:20124: a ho zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20125: gnang nas bshad pa ltar chos bshad par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20127: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK092(khe)001:20128: gsol ba btab ma thag pa de nas skyes bu
NK092(khe)001:20129: dam pa sems dpa' rdo rje nyid du gyur pa
NK092(khe)001:20130: badga gisa / ston pas dbang rtags su lag tu
NK092(khe)001:20131: rdo rje rgya gram bzhag pa de nyid bskor te
NK092(khe)001:20132: badga gisa / bsgyur nas / bla bkyal ba'i spobs
NK092(khe)001:20133: pa yod pas brjid baga tu gyur pa dang ldan
NK092(khe)001:20134: badga gisa / bsgyur nas / pas / rdo rje
NK092(khe)001:20135: theg pa bla na med pa'i don phul du byung
NK092(khe)001:20136: ba mtshon pa'i sgra tshiga tu ston pas kho bo
NK092(khe)001:20137: la ji skad bstan pa ltar smras te bshad par
NK092(khe)001:20138: badga gisa / bsgyur nas / pas / mdzad pa'o // de nyid gang zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:20140: a ho zhes pa yi ge gsum ni bshad zin te rgyud don ji lta ba bzhin dbang pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20141: de dag kyang 'dus pa'i 'khor lo rgyas par bshad
NK092(khe)001:20142: de dgyes pa'i yi ge a ho gnyis brjod pas
NK092(khe)001:20143: skye med la mnyes par mtshon pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20148: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20149: de rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i rgyal ba thams
NK092(khe)001:20150: cad kyi gdung rgyud du byung ba'i sras mchog chen
NK092(khe)001:20151: po de ni tshig tu brjod de canga mi gsung
NK092(khe)001:20152: pa nyid de / don gyi ngo bo brjod du med pas so //
NK092(khe)001:20153: de ltar ma gsungas pa nyid ni brjod pa thams
NK092(khe)001:20154: cad pa'i phyir gsung ngo bar mi rtog par bstan
NK092(khe)001:20155: pa thams cad du gsal bas zab cing rgya chera
NK092(khe)001:20156: brjod cing bashada de bka' stsal pa nyid do //
NK092(khe)001:20158: gang sngags theg pa chen po'i ngo bo tshig tu
NK092(khe)001:20159: bshad du med pa'i chosa nyid brjod pa dang bral
NK092(khe)001:20160: ba'i don gyi rgyud 'di nye bar bzung ba ni
NK092(khe)001:20161: 'das pa'i dus kyi rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK092(khe)001:20162: rnams kyis kyang tshig tu gsungs nas ma bshad de
NK092(khe)001:20163: / gsung zhing brjod du med pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20165: da ltar ston pa rigs kyi bdag po dang /
NK092(khe)001:20166: rgyal mchoga rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid kyang /
NK092(khe)001:20167: tshig tu brjod de rnam para bashada para mi bzheda
NK092(khe)001:20168: pas sprul pa'i sku ltar brjod pa tshig gi gsung
NK092(khe)001:20169: gis bka' stsal bar mi mdzad de /
NK092(khe)001:20170: rang gsal rig pa'i gsung mnga' bas byin gyi brlab
NK092(khe)001:20171: kyi tshul du gdul bya'i 'khor gyi rig pa la
NK092(khe)001:20172: don rgya chera bshad pa dang 'dra bar 'jal bar
NK092(khe)001:20173: byed pas dgongsa pas brgyud pa'am /
NK092(khe)001:20174: dgongs pa brda'i sgo nas chos ston pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20175: de yan chad ni chos sku dang longs sku'i bstan pa yang yin no //
NK092(khe)001:20177: gang rgyu rkyen dang bral bas dngos gzhi skye ba
NK092(khe)001:20178: meda pa'i chosa nyid kyi don yang dag par nges
NK092(khe)001:20179: pa ni / ngo bo mtha' gang du'ang 'byung ma
NK092(khe)001:20180: myong bar ma skyes pasa na rgyu 'bras yongs kyi
NK092(khe)001:20181: rtsa ba dang bcud kyi snying pora bashada par gsal
NK092(khe)001:20182: pa ni / te / des na snying po'i dona
NK092(khe)001:20183: gyi ngo bo ma nor ba'i gsang rgyud de kho
NK092(khe)001:20184: na nyid gang yina pa 'di ni brjod du med
NK092(khe)001:20185: pa nyid la brjod pas thog tu mi phebs pas
NK092(khe)001:20186: tshiga tu smra bar byas te bshad cing brjod du
NK092(khe)001:20187: yoda par rigs shing 'thad pa ma yina no //
NK092(khe)001:20188: de'i phyir tshig rgyas par spros te bshad pa nyid
NK092(khe)001:20189: na don ji bzhin pa'i thog tu mi phebs pas
NK092(khe)001:20190: 'khrul par gol ba yin no zhes rgyal ba rdzogs
NK092(khe)001:20191: pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang nges pa don gyi
NK092(khe)001:20192: mdo rgyud man ngag kun las yang dag par bshad
NK092(khe)001:20193: do // gtan tshigs de basa na ston pa rigs
NK092(khe)001:20194: kyi bdag po rdo rje rgyal po nyid yang tshig
NK092(khe)001:20195: tu phyung ste bka'a ma stsal bar /
NK092(khe)001:20196: kho bo la sogs pa la dgongas pa ting nge 'dzin gyis bshad de /
NK092(khe)001:20197: mnyam pa nyid gsang sngags don gyi rgya mtsho las mi g.yo bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20200: dgos pa'i yang dgos pa bshad pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20205: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20206: 'o na dgongs pa ji ltar brgyud zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:20207: gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i rgyud mchog rgyal ba'i
NK092(khe)001:20208: dgongsa pa mthar thug tu nges pa'i dona rnams ganga
NK092(khe)001:20209: dgongs pas gsal bar 'byina cing ston pa'i tshul bstan
NK092(khe)001:20210: pa yang / tshig gis brjod pas ma yin par /
NK092(khe)001:20211: dpe ji ltar na me longa g.ya' dwangs pa la gzugsa brnyan rang dbang med par 'byung ba ltar /
NK092(khe)001:20212: rgyal ba'i dgongsa pa snying po gsang ba'i don mchog
NK092(khe)001:20213: dam pa nyid sdud pa po dang 'khor gyi riga
NK092(khe)001:20214: pa dwangs pa la byin gyis brlabs kyis ranga snang
NK092(khe)001:20216: 'o na de yang tshig gis mtshon du med dam zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:20217: sgra tshig gis mi mtshon par dgongs pa'i don gyis mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20218: rgyud kyi ngo bo ma skyes pa'i chos nyid brjod
NK092(khe)001:20219: pa dang bral bas dngos gzhi snying po'i rtsa bar
NK092(khe)001:20220: gyur pa nyid dona gyis rang gsal du mtshon pas
NK092(khe)001:20221: ni tshiga tu brjod de spro ba ma yina pas
NK092(khe)001:20222: bshad pas mtshon par mi nus so //
NK092(khe)001:20223: ngo bo de ltar yin na'ang /
NK092(khe)001:20224: mi mthun pa ston pa ni dkri ba'i phyir tshig gis ston cing mtshon pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20225: de la gdul bya gang dag dkri bar bya zhe na /
NK092(khe)001:20226: zhen rtog gi mtshan ma ngang ma bral bas sgra
NK092(khe)001:20227: brjod yid la byed pa'i tshiga gi rnal 'byor pa
NK092(khe)001:20228: rnams / tshiga la brten nas snga ma'i rjes su
NK092(khe)001:20229: phyi ma long btags nas mthar chags su brjod de
NK092(khe)001:20230: zhib pa skad du zer yang de kho na la
NK092(khe)001:20231: 'chel bas dona gyi ngo bo'i mtha' yang ma mthong
NK092(khe)001:20232: bas don rtogs pa la rtsinga ste /
NK092(khe)001:20233: don mchog yal bar gyur pas na /
NK092(khe)001:20234: sgri'i tshiga gi phyir ram rjes su de la rtog
NK092(khe)001:20235: pa'i blo yi shes pa 'brangas pas gsang sngags kyi
NK092(khe)001:20236: gting mthong ba'i blo gros kyi rtsal zhana cing nus
NK092(khe)001:20238: gsang sngags la ldem dgongs kyis bakri zhing drang ba'i
NK092(khe)001:20239: thabs kyis tshig tu bstan pasa gsang don gyis yid
NK092(khe)001:20240: tshims nas bsam pa rangas te ngo bo'i mtha' mthong
NK092(khe)001:20241: bas don rtogs par bya'i zhes bya ba'i phyir du
NK092(khe)001:20242: / don mtshon du med cing mi dmigas pa la /
NK092(khe)001:20243: 'gro ba'i don du de nyid mtshon zhing dmigas pa
NK092(khe)001:20244: yi byin rlabs kyi rjod byed tshig dang sgra rgyud
NK092(khe)001:20245: 'di lta bu cho 'phrul chen pos tshiga gisa bstan
NK092(khe)001:20246: nas / gsang ba'i don gyi de kho na nyid
NK092(khe)001:20247: de mtshona par byas pas tshul bzhin du rtogs shing
NK092(khe)001:20248: goms par bya ba ni dgos ched do //
NK092(khe)001:20253: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20254: dgos pa'i yang dgos pa gang snyam pa la 'gyur
NK092(khe)001:20255: med bde ba chen po'i ngang du son pas bde
NK092(khe)001:20256: bar gshegsa pa rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi rgyal ba
NK092(khe)001:20257: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis
NK092(khe)001:20258: mtshan tha dad du grags pa kun gyi thugsa gasnga
NK092(khe)001:20259: ba'i ye shes brtag par dka' ba de nyid la
NK092(khe)001:20260: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pas snying po'i dona gyi
NK092(khe)001:20261: ngo bo bsgrub par bya ba'i don mchog blang dor
NK092(khe)001:20262: dang bral bas skye med mnyam pa nyid ni /
NK092(khe)001:20263: chos sku byang chub chen po zhes bya la /
NK092(khe)001:20264: ril go 'phang de la 'god pas thega pa chena po zhes kyang bya ste /
NK092(khe)001:20265: de lta bu'i mtshan nyid can gyi ma bsgribs gasla
NK092(khe)001:20266: bar kun la khyab cing bsnums pa'i chos nyid rang
NK092(khe)001:20267: bzhin gyi snang ba de'i don nyid lam pa gnas
NK092(khe)001:20268: pa kun gyis rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyi de
NK092(khe)001:20269: kho na nyid du mthonga bar bya ba dang /
NK092(khe)001:20271: thob par bya ba'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir /
NK092(khe)001:20272: de nyid mdon du gyur pa ni dgos pa'i yang dgosa pa mthar thug pa'o /
NK092(khe)001:20277: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20278: kho bo gsang ba'i bdag po ston pa dam pa nga nyid ni /
NK092(khe)001:20279: 'das pa dang da ltar dang ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK092(khe)001:20280: ga sum kun na bzhugs pa yi bde bar gshegs
NK092(khe)001:20281: pa'i rgyal ba kun gyi thugs gsang ba'i ye shes
NK092(khe)001:20282: kyi snying po rang bzhin 'od gsal ba nyid yin
NK092(khe)001:20283: te / des na ston pa bdag gis de lta
NK092(khe)001:20284: bu'i mtha' gang du'ang rnam pa can du snang ma
NK092(khe)001:20285: myong bas stong pa chen po mtha' bral ngo bo
NK092(khe)001:20286: gsal khyab kyi dbyings rang bzhin dag para sbas pa'i
NK092(khe)001:20287: chos nyid dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i gnas
NK092(khe)001:20288: lugs don gyi ngo bo nyid /
NK092(khe)001:20289: sus kyang mthong bar dka' ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK092(khe)001:20290: 'di yi don ma bcos pa'i rang bzhin du gnas
NK092(khe)001:20291: pa la mtshon byed mi 'dra ba'i thabs kyis don
NK092(khe)001:20293: mthun pa dang mi mthun pa'i rnam pas don la sbyor ba dpesa mtshona tshul dang /
NK092(khe)001:20294: lde'u miga rnam pa gsum la sogs pa'i rjod byed dag gisa mtshon nas /
NK092(khe)001:20295: skye med mnyam pa'i chos nyid gsang sngags ji bzhin
NK092(khe)001:20296: pa'i don rnal ma nyid rang gsal riga pa la
NK092(khe)001:20297: snang bar byas nas sgrib med du shar ba'i sgo
NK092(khe)001:20298: dabye bar 'osa pas de ltar ston pa po la
NK092(khe)001:20304: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20306: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs la gab cing sbas te
NK092(khe)001:20307: mngon du ma phyung ba gang mthar 'dzin can la
NK092(khe)001:20308: rang gsang thabs kyi chod pa'i chos nyid rgyud mchog
NK092(khe)001:20309: 'di yis mtshon bya don gyi ngo bo de nyid
NK092(khe)001:20310: de / de ltar brjod byar gyur pa gang de
NK092(khe)001:20311: tshig gi cho 'phrul gyis mtshona nas don gyi ngo
NK092(khe)001:20312: bo nyid nges par dbyung zhing gsal bar bya bar
NK092(khe)001:20314: ji bzhin par mtshon pa'i tshig sdebs legs pas gnas
NK092(khe)001:20315: lugs ma mthonga ba rnams la bstan para gsha' ba'am
NK092(khe)001:20316: / sde spar ltar na brjod de bshad pas /
NK092(khe)001:20317: mtshon bya'i don de nyid mthonga zhing rtogs pa na /
NK092(khe)001:20318: ngo bo ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhina nyid
NK092(khe)001:20319: du dngos po stobs zhugs kyi rigs pa mthar thug
NK092(khe)001:20320: pa'i lam nas 'thad par grub pa yin pas /
NK092(khe)001:20321: de ltar rigs pas mjal te 'dod pa'i don rtogs pa'o //
NK092(khe)001:20322: 'o na ston pa'i dgos 'brel las bstan pa'i dgos 'brel med do zhe na sngar /
NK092(khe)001:20323: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa 'di //
NK092(khe)001:20324: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du gsal //
NK092(khe)001:20325: zhes pas shin tu'ang yod de rdzogs par gsal nges so //
NK092(khe)001:20326: des na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi bstan mchog gsang
NK092(khe)001:20327: ba dam pa'i rang gi mtshan nyid ltar bshad na
NK092(khe)001:20328: yang / dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i mdo las /
NK092(khe)001:20329: khams gsum gnas pa'i sems can la //
NK092(khe)001:20330: mdo don 'di ltar gces pas na //
NK092(khe)001:20331: dgos pa zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK092(khe)001:20333: gzhan dag bde blag rtogs 'gyur bas //
NK092(khe)001:20334: mdo gzhan dag dang 'brel bar bshad //
NK092(khe)001:20335: mdo 'di dag la brten nas su //
NK092(khe)001:20336: dngos grub khyad par can yang thob //
NK092(khe)001:20337: des na dgos pa dag dang 'brel //
NK092(khe)001:20338: ting nge 'dzin dang byang chub sems //
NK092(khe)001:20340: sngags dang phyag rgya thugs rjes 'dul //
NK092(khe)001:20341: las dang dam tshig mdo yi don //
NK092(khe)001:20342: rnam bshad brjod pa zhes su bshad //
NK092(khe)001:20343: dngos grub 'bras bu khyad par can //
NK092(khe)001:20344: gdon mi za bar nges 'grub pa //
NK092(khe)001:20345: yang dgos yin par rgyal bas gsung //
NK092(khe)001:20346: de bas rnam pa bzhi po yis //
NK092(khe)001:20347: bde blag dag tu rtogs 'gyur phyir //
NK092(khe)001:20348: rnam bzhi khong du chud pa gces //
NK092(khe)001:20350: gsang ba'i rang gnad la brten nas chos nyid yongs
NK092(khe)001:20351: su rdzogs pa'i don gyi gsang ba ma nor bar
NK092(khe)001:20352: rnyed nas mtshan nyid rtogs pa la 'jug par bya'o
NK092(khe)001:20353: // dgos 'brel khyad par can dang ldan pa de
NK092(khe)001:20354: bas na ston pa gsang bdag chen po ngas bshad
NK092(khe)001:20355: do zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'i don to //
NK092(khe)001:20360: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK092(khe)001:20361: de skad cesa gasnga ba sngags kyi theg pa'i badga po sems dpa' rdo rje desa /
NK092(khe)001:20362: chosa thams cad 'dir dgosa 'brela yan lag 'dus para
NK092(khe)001:20363: ga cha bgosa te rgol ba pos mi tshugs par
NK092(khe)001:20364: mdzad de / gsang chen lung gi bstan pa gsal bar byas so //
NK092(khe)001:20365: de nasa langa ka'i badga po la sogas pa damna
NK092(khe)001:20366: pa'i lus kyi semas dapa'a rnams kyis kyang dgosa 'brel
NK092(khe)001:20367: yan lag bzhi'i sgo nas chosa thams cad blo la
NK092(khe)001:20368: yongsa su chub para gyur to //
NK092(khe)001:20370: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mado chen po las /
NK092(khe)001:20371: 'brela ba dgosa ched kyi yan lag rnam pa bzhir phye nas bstan pa'i le'u ste /
